headline: Health Canada Approves ELAHERE® for Certain Types of Platinum-Resistant Ovarian Cancers
summary: Today, AbbVie (NYSE: ABBV) has announced that under the Priority Review process, Health Canada has approved ELAHERE® (mirvetuximab soravtansine for injection), an antibody-drug conjugate (ADC), for the treatment of adult patients with folate receptor-alpha (FRα) positive, platinum-resistant epithelial ovarian, fallopian tube, or primary peritoneal cancer, who have received one to three prior systemic treatment regimens.1
